RESTAS-Yarc (Yet Another RESTAS Client)

Lightweight alternative to RESTAS-Client that uses the Clustericious framework.


Install the package:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install



Create a config file (~/etc/RESTAS.conf) that looks something like this:

---
url : http://localhost:10001
port : 10001
host : localhost
ssh_tunnel :
  remote_host : omidev.gsfc.nasa.gov
  server_host : devarch11
  server_port : '8300'



